ConnectorTestUtil.name: ConnectorTestUtil
ConnectorTestUtil.description: Enables developers to write Apex test classes for connectors used by the connected app provisioning solution. This class simulates provisioning for the associated app.

UserProvisioningLog.name: UserProvisioningLog
UserProvisioningLog.description: Provides methods for writing messages to monitor outbound user provisioning requests.

UserProvisioningPlugin.name: UserProvisioningPlugin
UserProvisioningPlugin.description: The UserProvisioningPlugin base class implements Process.Plugin for programmatic customization of the user provisioning process for connected apps.
